casebody.data:
Darien MARTINEZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
State of Florida DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE CHILD SUPPORT PROGRAM and Elizabeth C. De Los Santos, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1617 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this administrative appeal from the Florida Department of Revenue, Child Support Program is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 17, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
